Name: Country Hat
Short description: A cowboy hat is a hat that is usually worn by men in the Western United States. The cowboy hat is usually made of felt and typically has a crease in the crown. The brim is usually turned up in the front, to form a slight brim. The cowboy hat was originally made from animal fur, straw, or cloth.
